coworkers and my friends.

296
00:11:08,002 --> 00:11:11,137
Bev, Anna, this is Barney,
a high-functioning sociopath

297
00:11:11,138 --> 00:11:13,039
and my ex.

298
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:14,274
