for 14 hours a day...</i>

345
00:13:07,955 --> 00:13:09,255
<i>You have Super Mario Kart?!</i>

346
00:13:09,256 --> 00:13:11,524
Hell, yeah.

347
00:13:11,525 --> 00:13:13,660
But your mom doesn't need you.

348
00:13:13,661 --> 00:13:15,562
