360
00:13:48,462 --> 00:13:49,762
Hey, hey, sorry.
Oh, hi.

361
00:13:49,763 --> 00:13:51,130
Quick question.
Yeah.

362
00:13:51,131 --> 00:13:52,465
Why aren't you wearing purple
like your friends?

363
00:13:52,466 --> 00:13:54,968
Oh, I told them I forgot,
but the truth is,

364
00:13:54,969 --> 00:13:56,703
