371
00:14:07,414 --> 00:14:09,215
Oh, you're a gooey romantic,
too?

372
00:14:09,216 --> 00:14:11,684
Guilty. This is
embarrassing,

373
00:14:11,685 --> 00:14:15,088
but every year, I buy flowers
and a box of chocolates,

374
00:14:15,089 --> 00:14:17,290
